{"tid":1184131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝林鄭月娥","createTime":"2019-06-03T12:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T12:18:04.000Z","uid":129592,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c55e8f80574efa605c5114b29fa381845b6883","tid":1184131,"uid":129592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"屌 屋企人一直以黎都係盲撐政府<br />\n每次講政治都會講到燥<br />\n好似對牛彈琴咁 有耐性講都冇用<br />\n佢地覺得政府做嘢一定有佢嘅理由一定啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢講到心都淡 又唔想再因為咁成日嗌交<br />\n<br />\n但頭先食飯講起逃犯條例 同佢地講左成件事係點<br />\n之後佢地終於覺得政府係有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然6月9日佢地唔會企出黎<br />\n但係至少心態上已經唔同左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家<br />\n6月9號見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}